<h4><a href="https://www.cosmopolitan.com/tw/lifestyle/hot-topics/g33619713/starbucks-0817/">星巴克玉兔系列周边在中国台湾上市</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360229" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0820054.jpg" alt="" width="840" height="560" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0820054.jpg 840w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0820054-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0820054-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px" /></p>
